data.description: Contract Pending OPEN CANCELLEDUnique layout & backyard privacy are only 2 of the wonderful things about this house! Open & airy entry leading to the living room space with vaulted ceiling & cozy fireplace. The unobstructed layout opens directly to the eat-in kitchen w/natural light pouring in from large windows & patio door.  Eat in the updated kitchen or al'fresco on the deck overlooking the large backyard and open field. This unique plan splits the primary bedroom & two other bedrooms on opposite sides of the home. This split plan also allows for a spacious master bath w/double-sink vanity & closet! In addition to everything on the main floor, enjoy the additional finished recroom space in the basement to be turned into multi-use purposes: office area, exercise space, playroom or just a cozy area for gaming and movies!
